Ingredient: green bell pepper, seeded and chopped
shredded Colby Jack or Cheddar cheese
red onion, very thinly sliced and cut into 1-inch pieces
seafood seasoning (such as Old Bay®), or to taste
cooked kielbasa sausage, cut into 1 inch pieces
fresh corn, husks and silks removed
fresh okra pods, sliced 1/3 inch thick
white sugar or more to taste, divided
whipped topping (such as Cool Whip®), thawed
hot fudge ice cream topping, warmed
fresh peaches - peeled, pitted, and sliced
green bell peppers, cut into chunks
red bell pepper, cut into chunks
cayenne pepper (add more if you can stand it)
salt and ground black pepper to taste
fresh pineapple - peeled, cored and cut into 1-inch rings
thin chocolate cream sandwich cookies, such as Oreo Thins
cucumber, peeled, cut into small strips
fresh green beans, trimmed and snapped
creamy salad dressing (such as Miracle Whip™)
salt and ground black pepper to taste
fresh jalapeño chile pepper, finely chopped
